#people data
people=pd.read_csv('all_people_in_agreements_withManual.csv') #merged with PA-X data to give other datasets
overall_with_orgs2=pd.read_csv('persons_mentions_overall.csv') 
df_per_agr=pd.read_csv('per_org_agr_stage.csv')

#event data
#ucdp:
ucdp=pd.read_csv('gedevents-2021-12-02.csv')
u_actors=pd.read_csv('ucdp_total_events_actors_2011-21.csv')
ucdp_total_year=pd.read_csv('ucdp_actors_per_year.csv')
#acled:
acled=pd.read_csv('external data/2018-11-27-2021-12-02-Myanmar.csv')
